{"tid":2350283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【整合】港共試圖篡改歷史 一文回顧返2020年發生咩事","createTime":"2021-01-02T07:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T13:58:00.000Z","uid":142519,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"01232df84e47f2bec53a4f3b7bb920e920c1f604","tid":2350283,"uid":142519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:47:25.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">原文：</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100331115059955/posts/212401410519591/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100331115059955%2Fposts%2F212401410519591%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb04c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=a24ed2ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100331115059955/posts/212401410519591/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n#2020 #香港 #大事回顧 #歷史必須被記載 #請廣傳Share<br />\n2020對全世界來說都過得不易，武漢肺炎肆虐下，時間同時亦顯得更快、更為虛無。香港人繼續面對荒謬的事，不知爲何連「平安」都成了衆人的新年願望。<br />\n<br />\n讓我們回顧一下2020年發生了甚麼大事，藉此提醒港人不要習慣，保持信念，一起撐下去。<br />\n<br />\n即使不知道終點在哪裏，甚或是會不會看到終點; 只要大家相伴著，再嚴寒都會感受到溫暖。<br />\n<br />\n新一年，祝願大家在亂流下平安。<br />\n<br />\n－即使再幽暗 仍要有曙光<br />\n<br />\n整合/編: 杏仁露<br />\n_________<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/luminanthk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fluminanthk%2F&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb04c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=8e972e35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/luminanthk/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/luminanthk?igshid=1h4v7ruerwf4l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fluminanthk%3Figshid%3D1h4v7ruerwf4l&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb04c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=e604ad0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/luminanthk?igshid=1h4v7ruerwf4l</a><br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/luminanthktg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fluminanthktg&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb04c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=f2acd2ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/luminanthktg</a><br />\n讚好+追蹤+訂閱 = 支持幽光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3BUFPq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3BUFPq.jpg&h=64794a84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yxw5Nuw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyxw5Nuw.jpg&h=644df111&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nGqKiBg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnGqKiBg.jpg&h=9f38072b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gxtoy9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxtoy9D.jpg&h=50448ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Hj3y9J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Hj3y9J.jpg&h=26f938fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RPeyWn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRPeyWn6.jpg&h=2304660a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PzJzFPO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPzJzFPO.jpg&h=258cd6d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dxO4iBw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdxO4iBw.jpg&h=817f97ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efTWT9U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefTWT9U.jpg&h=b28554d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o6WUFPX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo6WUFPX.jpg&h=0e54a1f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCHTWoj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCHTWoj.jpg&h=59842ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fxVRH3n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfxVRH3n.jpg&h=6d724d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7Toy95.jpg\" data-thumb